      As you progress through the levels, you unlock access to bigger discounts on your insurance!üèÜ

    </div>
  </div>
<br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 fs-6">
      <strong>How is the cost of your car insurance policy calculated?</strong>
      <p class="mb-3 mt-3" style="line-height: 1.5;">
        The cost of the insurance premium is determined by your risk profile.
        By reducing speed in the TripQuest rewards zones you will be able to earn points and when you have enough points to level up, you will be offered discounts on your car insurance.
        Thanks to TripQuest, users can <strong>save up to 21%</strong> on their car policy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


